com.axeda.toolkit.ammp
Class CommunicatingAsset

java.lang.Object
  com.axeda.toolkit.ammp.CommunicatingAsset

public class CommunicatingAsset
extends Object

Class representing the identity and authentication credentials of the Asset communicating with the Platform. A CommunicatingAsset can be constructed as follows: 

      CommunicatingAsset asset = new CommunicatingAsset("model", "serial").withToken("unique and super secret");
